      "author": "mssoftjp",
      "description": "# Voice Input 0.9.2 Release Notes\r\n\r\n## Summary\r\nThis summarizes changes from 0.9.1 (2025-11-15, commit 88289ab) to 0.9.2 (commit c40db83).\r\n\r\n## Highlights\r\n- Harden draft saving: suppress errors when the draft folder already exists, warn only when the path is not a folder, and fall back from `vault.process` to `vault.modify` when updating existing files; on creation conflicts, re-fetch the file and retry saving. (ab368ee, 2f77ca9, 5fc7b50)\r\n- Stabilize view resolution: resolve the voice view via DeferredView using the view type instead of constructor name so minified builds work reliably. (dd65bcc)\r\n- Build/performance: strip comments from the AudioWorklet and fvad loader and sanitize embedded script generation. (4f41ee0)\r\n- Code quality: tighten ESLint rules and refactor logging/settings/security/view helpers. (6c81ba0)\r\n- Docs: add work attitude expectations to AGENTS.md. (738c726)\r\n- Version: bump manifest etc. to 0.9.2. (c40db83)\r\n\r\n",
